{"tid":2170298,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"世衛：建議十二歲或以上兒童佩戴口罩","createTime":"2020-08-23T07:24:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-23T07:56:33.000Z","uid":66271,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d8f6dd497c07f4e3b68393c3538afa29db991f34","tid":2170298,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T07:24:40.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】世界衛生組織就新型冠狀病毒發出新指引，建議所有十二歲或以上兒童要佩戴口罩。<br />\n<br />\n世衛與聯合國兒童基金會在世衛官方網頁上載文件指，有證據顯示十二歲或以上的兒童及青少年感染新冠病毒的風險與成年人相若，建議他們佩戴口罩及遵守保持一米社交距離。<br />\n<br />\n六至十一歲的兒童則可在成年人監察下，自行評估風險決定是否有需要戴口罩；至於五歲或以下小童，基於安全及對小童的整體利益考量，建議在正常情況下不需佩戴口罩。"},{"pid":"72d755ef2e163792b3808e3195dcedc260ce4575","tid":2170298,"uid":158128,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T07:26:20.000Z","msg":"不如下世先講"},{"pid":"a8d0aa849858704527ce9e7c946d924b1b7978f6","tid":2170298,"uid":330457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T07:27:25.000Z","msg":"點解係財經台<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b26a7317e524299f2956406224e1473cb4babb7","tid":2170298,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"72d755ef2e163792b3808e3195dcedc260ce4575","tid":2170298,"uid":158128,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T07:26:20.000Z","msg":"不如下世先講"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T07:27:43.000Z","msg":"佢講定10年後又有其他疫症要點做啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddfb48e43fab61619c2a71304f2e119a6563d597","tid":2170298,"uid":205043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T07:29:45.000Z","msg":"咁六十歲兒童呢"},{"pid":"7bcad615fbfd5aa425a7271013f9fa56dc162e1b","tid":2170298,"uid":55868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T07:30:04.000Z","msg":"五歲或以下小童，基於安全及對小童的整體利益考量，建議在正常情況下不需佩戴口罩。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nwhy<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c377a0307f6bb009749bcd14bfe014cd95957fc3","tid":2170298,"uid":27844,"lik